---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔹 1️⃣ Certification Status:-
Status	                 Meaning
Pending:-----------Campaign create hua, abhi run nahi hua.
In Progress:-------Campaign start ho chuka, reviewers review kar rahe hain.
Completed:---------Sab CertificationEntities ka review complete ho gaya.
Closed:------------Campaign officially close ho gaya.
Cancelled:---------Admin ne campaign cancel kar diya.
Failed:------------Campaign execution me koi error aaya.
🔹 2️⃣ CertificationEntity Status:-
Status	              Meaning
Pending:--------Entity review ke liye wait kar rahi hai
In Progress:----Reviewer ne review start kiya hai
Completed:------Entity ka review complete ho gaya
Approved:-------Reviewer ne approve kiya (item-wise)
Revoked:--------Reviewer ne access revoke karne ka decision diya
Escalated:------Reviewer ne timely decision nahi liya, escalation hua
🔹 3️⃣ CertificationItem Status:-
Status	             Meaning
Pending:------Item review ke liye wait kar raha hai
Approved:-----Reviewer ne approve kiya
Revoked:------Reviewer ne revoke kiya
Exception:----Item me koi issue ya exception aaya
Escalated:----Reviewer action nahi liya, item escalate hua
🔹 4️⃣ CertificationManager Status:-
Status	              Meaning
Active:-----Manager currently campaign ko monitor kar raha hai.
Inactive:---Manager temporarily inactive hai
Paused:-----Certification process temporarily paused hai
Completed:---Manager ke under sab campaigns complete ho gaye
🔹 5️⃣ CertificationSchedule Status:-
Status	            Meaning
Scheduled:---Campaign future me run hoga
Running:-----Campaign abhi chal raha hai
Completed:---Campaign successfully complete ho gaya
Cancelled:---Campaign cancel kar diya gaya.
